'''Nowa <U+015A>widnica''' is a village in the administrative district of [[Gmina Olszyna]], within [[Luba<U+0144> County]], [[Lower Silesian Voivodeship]], in south-western [[Poland]]. Prior to 1945 it was in [[Germany]].

